      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes, and appropriates funds for, the K\u016bpa\u02bba Law Enforcement Retention Bonus Program within the Department of Law Enforcement to provide retention bonuses to Department law enforcement officers for three years.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD1)"
    }
